{"tid":2103374,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜一度發電郵要求員工刪除TikTok","createTime":"2020-07-11T07:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T07:05:31.000Z","uid":81228,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0de7e5bfa873d8f358ec882f5da7d1519d96b5","tid":2103374,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"美國科網企業亞馬遜一度發電郵要求員工刪除應用程式TikTok，其後說是誤發。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜當地周五發內部電郵，說基於保安隱憂，要求員工即日從可以查看公司電郵的移動設備中刪除TikTok。但同日稍後改口說是錯誤發送電郵，重申目前對TikTok的政策無變。<br />\n<br />\nTikTok回應亞馬遜一度發出的內部電郵，表示事先沒有溝通，不明白他們的憂慮。又指近日針對TikTok的指控許多都是不正確或已過時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30034&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=e8209c82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30034&h=16655037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30034</a>"},{"pid":"7b6aaf9cb2405cf6fa691b1fa29371120520071e","tid":2103374,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"科技巨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e476bbd780bf18a3e10cf086a2c2415463e5d127","tid":2103374,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}